    <briefdescription>
<para>Analog axis calibration data structure. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Holds the calibration data for a single analog axis. Initial values are set from the devicetree and can be changed by the application in runtime using <ref refid="group__input__analog__axis_1gaae496bde41a58d92521b0a24f762caeb" kindref="member">analog_axis_calibration_set</ref> and <ref refid="group__input__analog__axis_1gad359f00fa9c46219a55a218d26d0407a" kindref="member">analog_axis_calibration_get</ref>. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
